        public boolean createPlanetarySystem​(java.lang.String starName,
                                     double temperature,
                                     double pressure,
                                     double humidity,
                                     double radiation)
        Creates a new planetary system with a star as the root
        Parameters:
        starName - The name of the star
        temperature - The temperature of the star in Kelvin
        pressure - The pressure of the star in Pascals
        humidity - Should be 0 for stars
        radiation - The radiation of the star in Sieverts
        Returns:
        True if successful, false otherwise

        Adds a planet to the planetary system with a chain structure
        Parameters:
        planetName - The name of the planet
        parentName - The name of the parent celestial object
        temperature - The temperature of the planet in Kelvin
        pressure - The pressure of the planet in Pascals
        humidity - The humidity of the planet as a percentage
        radiation - The radiation of the planet in Sieverts
        Returns:
        True if successful, false otherwise
